<paragraph id="FCADA5358DE8CE435EC3AFC9F5F45318" pageId="13" pageNumber="92">
Locality unknown. Specimen, (BMNH: ADP128624, male), labeled (
<normalizedToken id="34244B9B143D665B0D44A25F8C6CAE17" originalValue="Bates’">Bates'</normalizedToken>
